<lyrics>[V1]
 1- hạ ậty bṭyby fwq sẖʿrk .. hbny ạlận ạ̉ʿrf ḥq qdrk
 ʿwḍaⁿạ ʿn sẖwky fy ạ̹klylk .. wạtkỷn rạ̉sy ʿly̱ ṣdrk
